    <h3 id="section-8-2" class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mt-8 mb-4">8.2 Why Single-Tenant</h3>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      The RFP specifies multi-tenant architecture with active-active deployment, zero-downtime scaling,
      and cryptographic tenant binding. These are the right targets for a mature SaaS platform at scale.
      For a product launching with a small number of initial clients, this level of infrastructure is
      over-specified and adds cost without delivering proportional value.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      <strong>We propose single-tenant deployment: one isolated instance per client.</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
      <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
        <thead class="bg-[#1B2A4A] text-white">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-medium">Concern</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-medium">RFP Architecture (Multi-Tenant)</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-medium">Proposed Architecture (Single-Tenant)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Data isolation</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Row-level security in shared database</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Separate database per client &mdash; physical isolation</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Security assurance</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Depends on correct RLS implementation</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Guaranteed by infrastructure</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Auth complexity</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Multi-tenant Entra federation</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Single app registration per client</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Failure blast radius</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">One bug can affect all clients</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">An issue in one deployment cannot affect another</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Cost at 1&ndash;5 clients</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">~$1,200/month fixed</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">~$120&ndash;376/month (scales with clients)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Client onboarding</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Add tenant record, consent link, configure SP (~30 min)</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Provision infrastructure, deploy, configure DNS (~2&ndash;4 hours)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Migration path</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Already multi-tenant</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Migrate when client count justifies it (~18+)</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
