    <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-[#FF6B6B] pl-4 py-2 mb-4 bg-[#FFF5F5] rounded-r-lg">
      <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
        <strong>Why single-tenant now is cheaper:</strong> Multi-tenant architecture adds approximately
        15&ndash;25 person-days to the MVP build ($21,000&ndash;$35,000 AUD). It also commits Cloud9 to
        ~$1,200/month from day one. Single-tenant starts at ~$120/month. Over the growth period to 18
        clients, the cumulative saving is approximately $10,000&ndash;$15,000. Total cost of single-tenant
        now plus migration later is lower than multi-tenant upfront.
      </p>
    </blockquote>

