            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Network latency, serialisation, error handling</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">None &mdash; function calls are instant</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>API contract management</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Versioned contracts, backward compatibility, integration testing</td>
