            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Each service needs its own pipeline</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">None &mdash; one pipeline</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Infrastructure per service</strong></td>
